        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for copy [of <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>].</p>  
<p>Has now read Charles Bell’s book [<hi rend="italic">Anatomy and philosophy of expression</hi>, 3d ed. (1844)].</p> 
            <p>Reports instance of person, blind from birth, frowning, when supposedly the blind cannot control the muscle required.</p>
        </abstract>
